MatchedRegions.transcript: We conduct various experiments from different perspectives of the proposed information measure to show its properties.

MatchedRegion.Text: We conduct various experiments from different perspectives of the proposed information measure to show its properties. (e.g., backtracking intervals, threshold adjustment, poisoning capacity, and discrepancy measures)

MatchedRegions.transcript: And we also compare the performance of our DSC with the representative method.

MatchedRegion.Text: We compare the performance of DSC with the representative methods (AT, gradient clipping) to defend against accumulative poisoning attacks.
